claim.claim-text:
1. An optical device that scans with a laser beam on an image bearing member, comprising:
a laser beam source that emits a laser beam;
a reflecting means that has a plurality of reflecting members and reflects the laser beam emitted from said laser beam source;
a deflecting and scanning means that deflects and scans with the laser beam reflected by said reflecting means;
an adjusting means that moves at least part of said reflecting members, and adjusts the size of the laser beam entering the deflecting scanning means; and
an optical component for irradiating the image bearing member with a laser beam,
wherein the adjusting means changes said size of the laser beam according to the temperature of the optical component.
